title.narrative: Contribution to European Fund for Sustainable Development

description.narrative: European Fund for Sustainable Development (EFSD) is the key pillar of EU's External Investment Plan (EIP). The aim of the EFSD is to promote economic growth and employment in EU partner countries. Under the project, Denmark provides DK 75 mill. to EFSD.
